      "term": "screening",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "A2",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "the process of examining or testing someone or something to decide suitability or quality",
          "examples": ["The screening of applicants will start next week.", "A medical screening is recommended for adults over 50."],
